      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      rf-mms-cod-dpz       to   w-rip-sdo-esu-sdz      .
           move      rf-mms-tip-mag       to   w-rip-sdo-esu-stm      .
           move      rf-mms-num-mag       to   w-rip-sdo-esu-snm      .
           move      rf-mms-var-mag       to   w-rip-sdo-esu-svm      .
           move      rf-mms-cod-dsl       to   w-rip-sdo-esu-sds      .
       rip-sdo-esu-100.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Determinazione saldo di fine anno           *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Saldo a inizio anno                     *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      rf-mms-qta-ini       to   w-rip-sdo-esu-wsd      .
