           move      w-rip-sdo-esu-snm    to   rf-mmz-num-mag         .
           move      w-rip-sdo-esu-svm    to   rf-mmz-var-mag         .
           move      w-rip-sdo-esu-stc    to   rf-mmz-tip-ctm         .
           move      w-rip-sdo-esu-scm    to   rf-mmz-cod-ctm         .
