           move      rf-mmz-num-mag       to   w-rip-sdo-esu-snm      .
           move      rf-mmz-var-mag       to   w-rip-sdo-esu-svm      .
           move      rf-mmz-tip-ctm       to   w-rip-sdo-esu-stc      .
           move      rf-mmz-cod-ctm       to   w-rip-sdo-esu-scm      .
           move      rf-mmz-tip-arc       to   w-rip-sdo-esu-sta      .
           move      rf-mmz-cod-arc       to   w-rip-sdo-esu-sca      .
