                                               rn-dat-inv             .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Scrittura record [datinv]                   *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      "PT"                 to   f-ope                  .
           move      "pgm/mag/num/ioc/obj/indatinv"
                                          to   s-pat                  .
